@startuml
autonumber
actor "ATCC/Admin" as ATCC
participant "AircraftController" as Ctrl
participant "CalculateAircraftOperationalHoursUseCase" as UC
participant "AircraftRepository" as Repo
database "Database" as DB

ATCC -> Ctrl : GET /api/aircrafts/operational-hours
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> UC : execute()
activate UC

UC -> Repo : findAll()
activate Repo

Repo -> DB : SELECT * FROM aircrafts
activate DB
DB --> Repo : list of all aircraft instances
deactivate DB

Repo --> UC : fleetList
deactivate Repo

note right of UC: Iterates over entities.\nExtracts registrationNumber and\ntotalFlightHours for each aircraft.

UC -> UC : map to List<AircraftOperationalHoursResponse>

UC --> Ctrl : hoursResponseList
deactivate UC

Ctrl --> ATCC : 200 OK (JSON Collection)
deactivate Ctrl
@enduml